represented the KingaEuro(TM)s Return to _Berlin_, by that of _Jason_, after the
Conquest of the Golden Fleece.

After some other Festivals of this nature, occasionaEuro(TM)d by the public Joy,
the Court separated, when the King set out for _Oranjebourg_[4], and the
