that she obtainaEuro(TM)d the KingaEuro(TM)s Consent to the Marriage, which was celebrated
some time after at _Lutzelbourg_.

Much about this time we had a new Ceremony in our Climates. This[8] was
the Erection of a Statue which the King causaEuro(TM)d to be set up in honor of
his Father _Frederic-William_ the Great. aEuro(TM)Tis perfectly like that of
