It represented a Temple of an Oval Form, whose Roof was supported by
Pillars of the _Corinthian_ Order, between each of which were placaEuro(TM)d
Statues that represented the QueenaEuro(TM)s Vertues. In the middle of the
Cataphalque just in the Upright there was a Glory, in which there was the
