Ailment; so that his Physicians advisaEuro(TM)d him to make use of the Waters
of_Carlsbadt_ in _Bohemia_; and at the beginning of the fine Season, his
Majesty went thither accordingly.

The KingaEuro(TM)s Departure being resolvaEuro(TM)d on, I beggaEuro(TM)d his MajestyaEuro(TM)s leave, to
make the Campaign in _Flanders_ in quality of a Voluntier. I set out from
