which when they had rubbaEuro(TM)d it about his Nose, died that Instant. Thus was
God pleasaEuro(TM)d to preserve this Hero from the basest of Treasons.

I wishaEuro(TM)d I could have been at the taking of _Lisle_, but was obligaEuro(TM)d to
