Her Majesty likewise granted the same Honor to several other Ladies, to
whom she gave an Invitation by a Gentleman when they were in the Circle.

aEuro(TM)Twas at the time of the KingaEuro(TM)s Marriage that I lost my Father-in-law: I
was very much concernaEuro(TM)d for his Death, especially on account of the
