Coffee-coloraEuro(TM)d Velvet, adornaEuro(TM)d with Jewels, to the Value of several
Millions. The young Dauphin was at his MajestyaEuro(TM)s Right Hand in a Robe of
Gold Brocade, adornaEuro(TM)d with Diamonds and Pearls. The Duke of _Orleans_ was
on his Left, dressaEuro(TM)d in a Suit of blue Velvet, adornaEuro(TM)d with a Gold
_Spanish_ Point, seeded with very beautiful Diamonds and Pearls. The
