that every body wishaEuro(TM)d publickly that he was gone.

I have had the Honor to acquaint you, that the Electoral Prince of
_Saxony_ was at the _Persian_aEuro(TM)s Audience. This Prince had been for some
time in _France_; and thoaEuro(TM) he was _incog._ by the Name or Title of the
